snippet.title: Super Stardust™ Delta Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The reviews are in and Super Stardust Delta is a hit!  See what the critics are saying about the latest iteration of the bestselling franchise on PSN. With brand-new features made specifically for PlayStation®Vita, players continue to destroy everything in their sight. Create black holes, launch swarm missiles and unleash shockwaves with all-new PlayStation®Vita controls.

Key Features:
o Precise Twin Stick controls.
o New controls, mechanics and enemies designed specifically for PlayStation®Vita.
o All modes from Super Stardust HD and Super Stardust Portable plus new modes and challenges for PlayStation®Vita.

http://us.playstation.com/games-and-media/games/super-stardust-hd-ps3.html

©2011 Sony Computer Entertainment Europe.  Super Stardust is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment Europe. Developed by Housemarque OY.

Full HD 1080p requires an HDMI cable and a 1080p native display with an HDMI input supporting HDCP.  Video out in HD requires cables and an HD compatible display, both sold separately.  This video will play displays ranging from standard definition to 1080p.
